Package: tidyamplicons
Type: Package
Title: Functions to Manipulate and Visualize Amplicon Sequence Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Stijn Wittouck
Description: These functions are an alternative to, or at least complementary to the
    phyloseq package. They are based on the tidy data pardigm and allow for
    easier, more intuitive data access, processing and visualization. Especially
    if you like the tidyverse way of working with data.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    tidyverse,
    stringr,
    vegan,
    phyloseq
